News.Title: AGI Infra Launches Urbana Square Commercial Project
News.Summary: AGI Infra Limited announced the launch of Urbana Square, a commercial project in Jalandhar, Punjab, featuring 142 commercial shops and 218 office spaces. Bookings commenced January 03, 2026.

News.Title: AGI Infra Appoints Book Running Lead Manager for QIP
News.Summary: AGI Infra Limited's board approved appointment of Aryaman Financial Services Limited as Book Running Lead Manager for its Qualified Institutional Placement issue during meeting held on January 03, 2026.

News.Title: AGI Infra Gets RERA Nod for Urbana Square Project
News.Summary: AGI Infra Limited receives RERA approval for its commercial project 'Urbana Square' in Jalandhar, marking a significant milestone in the company's real estate development portfolio.

News.Title: AGI INFRA Reports Strong Q2 Growth with 26% Jump in Net Profit
News.Summary: AGI INFRA delivered robust quarterly performance with net profit rising 26% to 220.5M rupees and revenue growing 10% to 853M rupees year-over-year. The company's EBITDA margin expanded significantly to 39.42% from 34.32%, indicating improved operational efficiency and profitability.

News.Title: AGI Infra Receives Approval to Raise Up to 5 Billion Rupees
News.Summary: AGI Infra has received approval for fundraising activities with a limit of up to 5 billion rupees. The approval enables the company to proceed with its capital raising plans.
